{"tid":108382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]不見外置充電器　躁父竹棍打死16歲兒子","createTime":"2017-02-05T08:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T09:06:20.000Z","uid":32407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6faf0da30912669b97ec309672d2eb0faca31adf","tid":108382,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170205/bkncn-20170205121129657-0205_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170205%2Fbkncn-20170205121129657-0205_05011_001.html&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=cc28b4a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170205/bkncn-20170205121129657-0205_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n廣西貴港市港南區橋圩鎮人一名52歲周姓男子，近日因懷疑自己的手機外置充電器被16歲的兒子阿強拿走，一氣之下竟用竹棍毆打兒子的頭部、手臂等部位，最終兒子被發現倒斃於茅屋之中，疑因傷重不治。目前周男已被當地警方刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上月25日凌晨零時許，周男外出遊玩回家後，發現自己的手機外置充電器不見。他看見兒子躺在床上，疑外置充電器是被兒子拿走，惟兒子卻否認。周男認為，家中只有自己和兒子兩人，充電器不可能被別人拿走。一氣之下，竟拿起竹棍毆打兒子的頭部和手臂。<br />\n<br />\n當日上午，周男起床做早餐，發現兒子不在家後未在意。直到翌日下午，一名村民發現阿強倒在一間茅草屋內遂通知周男，周男隨即將兒子抬回家。當地救護人員接報到場，惟檢查發現阿強已死亡。據悉，阿強被打後躲進茅草屋，直到翌日下午才被發現。事後周男向當地警方自首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7fce0a1ff2791f51ce6735f52e81110665123f","tid":108382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"df66b7e77e94a086c7c3b660b39fa5eb1a70b808","tid":108382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249ca41b40f2d076c25218b811cc4b7d3eda237a","tid":108382,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係30CM長既法包，有D失敗"},{"pid":"1c14c23fb9686b8381f09b6722b8417d7bdcbaa9","tid":108382,"uid":10559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c2d1994974c7bc17db14f8aa98c895df6da7b9","tid":108382,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"潮文一到強國，即變現實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25557c172ead1529a521790f400b0ff12bf065d","tid":108382,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"咁個叉電器搵到未"}]}